command
-------
php composer.phar require zendframework/zftool:dev-master

description
-----------
the above command will install zftool.phar in the location
php vendor/zendframework/zftool

command
-------
php php vendor/zendframework/zftool/zf.php

description
-----------
will show the list of things this tool can do


command
-------
php vendor/zendframework/zftool/zf.php create module Album

description
-----------
The above command will create a module named Album

command
-------
php vendor/zendframework/zftool/zf.php create controller Index Album

description
-----------
The above command will create a controller named Index in the Album Module

command
-------
php vendor/zendframework/zftool/zf.php create action add Index Album

description
-----------
The above command will create an action named add in the Index Controller of the Album Module
Also it will create the corresponding action

